title: Voom:Voom
text:
Voom:Voom is an Austrian electronica group consisting of Christian Prommer, Roland Appel (of the groups Fauna Flash and Tr√ºby Trio) and Peter Kruder of Kruder & Dorfmeister.
Their first full-length album, PengPeng, was released on April 24, 2006, on Studio !K7 records.  They had previously released four EPs.
